primary_outcome.description:
Danger signs or severe malaria on day 1, 2 or 3, in the presence of parasitemia;
Parasitemia on day 2 higher than on day 0, irrespective of axillary temperature;
Parasitemia on day 3 with axillary temperature ≥ 37.5 °C; and
Parasitemia on day 3 ≥ 25% of count on day 0.
